channel.title: What source has the cleanest commands?
channel.description:
[i]I know that there are some sources that say they only have certain commands, but when I look in the client.java, there are about 20 other commands. Most of them are personalized with their friends names etc.[/i]
[b]Can somebody redirect me to a source that has only basic ban/kick ones but at the same time not all the pointless commands? [/b]
I just want a basic source that I can add stuff without having to remove stuff.
Thanks, TankedJare
